response.original_title: IMPACT Wrestling: One Night Only: Clash in the Bluegrass
response.overview: This March, IMPACT Wrestling presents One Night Only: Clash in the Bluegrass, in partnership with Ohio Valley Wrestling, from Davis Arena in Louisville, Kentucky, USA. In a 3 Way match for the IMPACT World Championship, Johnny Impact defends against Eddie Edwards and Adam Revolver. The OVW Heavyweight Title is also up for grabs, as Tony Gunn defends against Sami Callihan, who will have his oVe disciples by his side. The War Kings, Crimson and Jax Dane, face off against King's Ransom and The Void in a 3 Way match for the OVW Southern Tag Team Titles. Plus Brian Cage battles Justin Smooth, Madison Rayne meets Cali Young and in a 4 Way match, it's Moose vs. Jay Bradley vs. Cash Flo vs. Big Zo.
response.title: IMPACT Wrestling: One Night Only: Clash in the Bluegrass
